name: Eyare
description: $Eyare was a 2 year old western lowland gorilla at the Calgary Zoo, born on 20th April, 2022, to mother Dossi and father Jasiri. She unexpectedly passed away during a move within the gorilla enclosure on 12th November 2024 and we are fighting for her justice just like we did with HARAMBE. Now, with $Eyare laid to rest we are spreading her phenomenon across web3 and the entire space of the crypto currency world.
